high_descs: Turn right and walk to the door then turn right and walk to the tomato on the counter to your left turning left to face it when you get to it.
Pick up the potato that's in front of you to the right of the tomato.
Turn right and take a step then turn right to face the fridge.
Chill the potato in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the garbage that's to the right of the fridge turning left to face it when you get there.
Put the potato in the garbage that's in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold potato in the garbage.

high_descs: walk to face the kitchen island
pick up the potato from the kitchen island
turn around to face the fridge
open the fridge door, put the potato into the fridge, close the door, wait, open the door, pick up the potato from inside fridge, close the door
walk to the right to face the garbage can on the right of the fridge
put the potato into the garbage can
anns.task_desc: put a chilled potato into a kitchen garbage can

high_descs: Go to the bin on the right of the fridge
Put the potato in the bin
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled potato in a bin
